{"id":140967,"type":6,"name":"Zack Snyder's Justice League","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/81/d6/140967_ZhJoZ.jpg","summary":"　　2017年，导演扎克·斯奈德（Zack Snyder）在痛失华裔养女 秋·斯奈德（Autumn Snyder）之后不得不离开投入心血制作的《正义联盟》，华纳公司随后让乔斯·韦登（Joss Whedon）接手此片的编导，并将四个小时的拍摄素材缩减到了两个小时。这些在上映前相继换掉导演、配乐师和编剧等人员的行为，最终导致一部半成品的上映。\r\n　　在乔斯·韦登这部碎片化版本的《正义联盟》上映并经历平淡的反响之后，HBO Max于2020年授予了扎克·斯奈德2000-3000万美元的预算，以按他的自己的意愿来完成电影，使得这部万众期待的导演剪辑版本得到了重见天日的机会。 ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>扎克·施奈德版正义联盟</li><li><span>原作: </span>Detective Comics、<a href=\"/person/24742\">DC Comics</a></li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/13968\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">Zack Snyder</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>4</li><li><span>开始: </span>2021</li><li><span>类型: </span>动作 / 科幻</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>60分钟</li><li><span>电视网: </span>HBO MAX</li><li><span>首播国家: </span>美国</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt12361974</li><li><span>编剧: </span>Zack Snyder / Chris Terrio</li><li><span>主演: </span>Ben Affleck / Henry Cavill / Gal Gadot / Ezra Miller / Jason Momoa / Ray Fisher</li><li><span>别名: </span>正义联盟导演剪辑版</li>","collection":{"wish":17,"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"DC","count":5},{"name":"电影","count":4},{"name":"DC拓展宇宙","count":1},{"name":"超级英雄","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":550130,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/550130","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":989356,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/989356","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":989357,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/989357","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":989358,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/989358","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"crt":[{"id":43963,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a6/bc/43963_crt_fNJI5.jpg","name":"神奇女侠","desc":"主角"},{"id":43964,"image